6 2ng files and 6 0.2ng files Samples are QC Hela standard (https://www.thermofisher.com/order/catalog/product/88328#/88328). LC system: Pump + Autosampler:Thermo Scientific Dionex UltiMate 3000 Series Column i.d. 30 um with different packing material: J3 = Jupiter C18, 3.0 um, 300 angstrom, 50 cm long K13 = Kinetex C18,1.3 um, 100 angstrom, 9cm long W17 = Water BEH C18, 1.7 um, 130 angstrom, 16 cm long 60 min separation gradient (8%B to 25%B) 20 min flushing from 25%B to 45%B 5 min washing from 45% to 90%B 25 min regeneration at 2% flowrate is about 30-40 nL/m. Mobile A = Water (Honeywell) + 0.1 % Formic Acid (Thermo). Mobile B = Acetonitrile (Honeywell) + 0.1% Formic Acid (Thermo). The file names contain the sample size and lc packing material.
